            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Arphocras <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Sulpici Galbae unctor se vivo locum emit sibi et <lb n="2"/>Corintho denaris XXC et ossuarium denaris CLXXV </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Arphocras <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Sulpici <lb n="2"/>Galbae <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ervus</ex></expan> unctor </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Corinthus <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Sulpici <lb n="2"/>Galbae <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ervus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XXV </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Faustus <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Galbae <lb n="2"/>a manu <lb n="3"/>ollam donavit <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Sulpicius Arpocras
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die insgesamt 4 Inschriften verteilen sich auf den Architrav, die Fläche unter der linken Büste, die Fläche unter der rechten Büste und den Sockel der Ädikula. (B): AE 1980: Z. 6/7: keine Angabe des Zeilenfalls. C. Sulpicius Galba: wohl Verwandter des Kaisers Galba.</p>
            </div>
